            <title>[AMQ-4307] org.apache.activemq.transport.http.HttpClientReconnectTest hangs occasionally</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-4307</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This test occasionally hangs, causing the build to hang.  I haven&apos;t been able to reproduce it yet, but have seen it several times on the Fuse Hudson instance.  I&apos;ll attach a patch which adds a timeout.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
